      "acceptanceCriteria": "Qualitative mapping of simulation inputs to experimental conditions is sufficient at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "A parameter equivalency table confirms that all CFD boundary conditions are set to match experimental values within documented tolerances. Formal equivalency uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2."
    }
