    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out under MRL 2 provisions of ASME V&V 40-2018. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass conditions at the flow rates and rotational speeds defined in the requirement binding. No weakeners were identified during review.",
